### Test Remita Endpoints

### 1. Get All Billers
GET https://localhost:7001/api/v1/send/api/bgatesvc/v3/billpayment/billers
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Biller Products
GET https://localhost:7001/api/v1/send/api/bgatesvc/v3/billpayment/biller/QADEMO/products
Content-Type: application/json

